snippet.title: Easy Red 2: Trailer 1.3 - Upcoming Kos Rework and Tunisia Campaign
snippet.description:
Kos Rework and Tunisia free campaign are coming by the first half of 2024.
Easy Red 2 is currently available on Steam, Xbox and nintendo Switch.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1324780/Easy_Red_2/
